    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a source of parts. The engine requires significant mechanical work to be roadworthy, and the transmission shows signs of slipping. Externally, there is widespread paint oxidation, several large dents, and noticeable rust on the rocker panels. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and several missing trim pieces. It is being sold strictly 'as-is,' and we recommend towing it from the lot.",
