    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a solid foundation for someone looking for a reliable but lived-in car. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car would benefit from a tune-up and some routine maintenance in the near future. The exterior has visible clear coat peeling on the hood and roof, along with several minor dings and scratches from daily use. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and a few small tears, but all major electronics and climate controls remain operational. It\u2019s a dependable choice for a budget-friendly commuter or a first car.",
      "price": 20500.0,
