    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and I think you're going to love it. It's been such a reliable companion for me, always getting me where I need to go with no fuss! It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-maintained over the years\u2014definitely ready to hit the road with a new owner. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that still has tons of life left in it, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant, utilizing VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing and lift. Power is managed through a G96 6-speed manual transaxle, ensuring a direct mechanical connection. Crucial preventative maintenance is documented, including an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a proactive rear main seal (RMS) replacement. The naturally aspirated engine exhibits strong compression and a clean bore-scope profile. The chassis remains taut with its original multi-link rear geometry and MacPherson strut front end, while the braking system utilizes four-piston monoblock calipers for exceptional thermal management. This is a highly communicative, driver-spec 911 that balances analog feedback with modern performance metrics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Interior is clean. Mechanically sound. Title ready for transfer.",
      "price": 32000.0,
